    <title>Activities</title>
    <p>Test</p>
    <p>Activities go here! Don't forget to put text in <c>&lt;p&gt;</c> tags or it won't show up.</p>

    <activity xml:id="activity-2-1">
        <introduction>
          <p>A water balloon is tossed vertically from a fifth story window. It's height <m>h(t)</m>, in meters, at a time <m>t</m>, in seconds, is modeled by the function
            <md>
              <mrow>h(t)=-5t^2+20t+25 \amp </mrow>
            </md>
          </p>
        </introduction>
        <task> <p>Complete the following table.
          <table>
            <tabular>
              <row header="yes" bottom="minor" >
                <cell><m>t</m></cell> 
                <cell><m>h(t)</m></cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>0</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>1</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>2</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>3</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>4</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>5</cell>
              </row>
            </tabular>
          </table>
        </p>
        </task>
        <task> <p>Explain why <m>h(t)</m> is not a linear function.</p>
        </task>
        <task><p> What is the meaning of <m>h(0)=25</m>?</p>
          <ol marker="A." cols="1">
            <li><p> the initial height of the water balloon is 25 meters.</p></li>
            <li><p> the water balloon reaches a maximum height of 25 meters. </p></li>
            <li><p> the water balloon hits the ground after 25 seconds.</p></li>
            <li><p> the water balloon travels 25 meters before hitting the ground.</p></li>
        </ol> </task>
        <task>
          <p> Find the vertex of the quadratic function.
            <ol marker="A." cols="2">
              <li><p><m>(0,25)</m> </p></li>
              <li><p> <m>(2,45)</m> </p></li>
              <li><p> <m>(5,0)</m> </p></li>
              <li><p> <m>(1,40)</m></p></li>
          </ol>     
          </p>
        </task>
        <task> <p>What is the meaning of the vertex?
          <ol marker="A." cols="1">
            <li><p> The water balloon reaches a maximum height of 25 meters at the start.</p></li>
            <li><p> After 2 seconds, the water balloon reaches a maximum height of 45 meters. </p></li>
            <li><p>After 5 seconds, the water balloon reaches a maximum height. </p></li>
            <li><p> After 1 second, the water balloon reaches a maximum height of 40 meters.</p></li>
        </ol>     
        </p>
        </task>
      </activity>
